  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Inclusive secondary education support for all the poor/orphans and vulnerable children with disability, and adolescent girls in targeted communities of Chipangali District.  Education is central to all and especially to women in the fight against poverty and discrimination. However access to education by the girl child and children with disabilities in Chipangali district is low. This is because of several reasons. The first cause is poverty itself.</narrative>
